    MAYBE_SET(RC_UNDERLINE_LINKS,       LYUnderlineLinks,   MSG_ENABLE_LYNXRC),
    PARSE_ENU(RC_USER_MODE,             user_mode,          tbl_user_mode, N_("\
user_mode specifies the users level of knowledge with Lynx.  The\n\
